-------------------------
Version 0.06 (2008-04-13)
-------------------------

* wrap 'require Encode' in an eval {} within the
  unicode test
* set a license tag in Makefile.PL

-------------------------
Version 0.05 (2008-01-11)
-------------------------

* make XS _getval() unicode aware

-------------------------
Version 0.04 (2004-04-04)
-------------------------

* use DynaLoader instead of XSLoader

* XS part is now optional, no C compiler needed

* Scalar::Util is no longer a prerequisite

-------------------------
Version 0.03 (2004-03-31)
-------------------------

* improved handling of styles

-------------------------
Version 0.02 (2004-03-31)
-------------------------

* the update method wasn't compatible with
  Scrolled widgets, changed to data method

* data can now also be configured using
  configure(-data => $data);

* added styles for normal and node items

* all styles are now advertised subwidgets

-------------------------
Version 0.01 (2004-03-30)
-------------------------

* initial release

